+/*
+ *  IBM eServer eHCA Infiniband device driver for Linux on POWER
+ *
+ *  Firmware calls
+ *
+ *  Authors: Christoph Raisch <raisch@de.ibm.com>
+ *           Hoang-Nam Nguyen <hnguyen@de.ibm.com>
+ *           Waleri Fomin <fomin@de.ibm.com>
